<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <title>Email-Template1</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Mulish:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    p,
    span {
      color: #132222 !important;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="main-div" style="background-color: #f5f6f7; width: 80%; margin: auto; padding: 30px">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="header-div">          
          <h6 class="" style="
                font-weight: bold;
                color: rgba(31, 31, 31, 0.7);
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-top: 15px;
                font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;
              ">
            Enabling Research Accessibility for Everyone
          </h6>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="content-div" style="border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(196, 196, 196)">
          <div style="background-color: white; padding: 25px">
            <h1 style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;color: #00b159;">
              Confirm your email with the following code
            </h1>
            <p style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif">
              Thank you for signing up for Boombolt. Weâ€™re happy that you are here.
            </p>
            <p style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif">
              Enter the following code to activate your account and access your dashboard. 
            </p>
            <div style="text-align: center">
              <span style="
                      font-size: 34px;
                      display: inline-block;
                      margin-top: 20px;
                      margin-bottom: 20px;
                    ">
                  <span><%= emailTemplate?.otp?.substr(0,3) %></span><span style="background: #132222;
                  height: 3px;
                  width: 10px;
                  display: inline-block;
                  vertical-align: middle;"></span><span><%=emailTemplate?.otp?.substr(3,6)%></span>
                </span>
            </div>
            <p style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif; margin-top: 20px">
              Should you have any problems or questions, please do not hesitate
              to ask us.
              <a style="
                    font-weight: bold;
                    text-decoration: underline;
                    color: #2377db;
                  " href="">Have queries? Ask us.
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="footer-div">
          
          <p style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif; margin-top: 0px;">
            This email was sent to
            <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #00b159" href="">
              <%= emailTemplate?.user?.email %>
            </a>
          </p>
          <a style="
                font-weight: bold;
                text-decoration: underline;
                font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif;
                color: #2377db;
              " href="#">View and Manage </a><span style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif">your subscription
            online.</span>
          <p style="font-family: 'Mulish', sans-serif">
            You're receiving this because you've signed up for a new account.
            Your given data is processed by Boombolt. All the data security
            protocol are strictly in place. You have the right to access,
            modify, rectify and delete these data. Check out our complete
            <a style="font-weight: bold; color: #2377db" href="<%= appUrl %>/privacy-policy">Privacy
              Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>